social_posts.post_text: I love connecting with genuine people and one of the main things i’m enjoying while being in this wonderful world or art, is seeing the people I can impact when it comes to changing someones mood or a vibe in the atmosphere. I enjoy being happy, and I love making other people happy because you never know what the next person is going through. Quantity was what I wanted to focus on when I first started but getting those DM’s and messages from those few special people that choose to rock out with the vibes are what really matter. Even if it’s just 100 people I can impact and somehow make them smile, feel a little more confident, or make their day better is a purpose I can rock with on and off the field… 🤍🎵🦄

This song is a mixture of how I’m going about doing things in the future moving on & some from how I felt in the past when I was in a mental space of feeling fed up about other peoples opinion on my personality and how I should act. People that didn’t even know me were constantly questioning my every move as if my intentions were i’ll when in reality, i’m one of the the most fun, loving, open minded people you could ever meet. I just didn’t conform!
Their judgment made me feel a certain type of way at first…but staying true to myself is what matters most- and that’s why I called this song No Regrets.

Im super excited for this to drop on New Years! Starting 2023 off right!
